## 10. Risks & Mitigations
| Risk | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|
| Deadline | Prioritize reveal loop; testnet only. |
| OneWallet Bugs | Fallback email login; Discord support. |
| Low Rares | Adjustable RNG seed. |

